name: The Jungle Bunch: To the Rescue
original_name: Les As de la Jungle à la rescousse !
overview: Maurice, a penguin raised in the jungle who thinks he is a tiger, leads a group of misfit animals on missions to rescue their fellow animals, no matter what their trouble is.

episodes.name: Deep Into the Chasm
episodes.overview: Professor Ernest, a kiwi, comes to the Jungle Bunch because the earth tremor which has just occurred has opened up a large crack right in the middle of his village! He needs the Jungle Bunch to fix it.

episodes.name: The Boulder of Fear
episodes.overview: Elephants are bullied by a so-called ghost. Hidden behind a rock, the ghost asks them to give him all their fruits as an offering. The Bunch will soon discover that the ghost is just a very special animal - a chameleon.

episodes.name: Rubies Are Forever
episodes.overview: Melina, a former love of Gilbert when he was young, hijacked the rubies of the jungle to create a kind of malefic laser. She wants to take possession of the jungle and the lair of the Jungle Bunch.

episodes.name: The Bloody Berry
episodes.overview: A beautiful red fruit causes a turtle to go into a deep sleep that's impossible to wake from. Meanwhile, Batricia also discovers the fruit to use as lipstick.

episodes.name: The Invasion Has Begun
episodes.overview: Flamingos think horseshoe crabs are aliens bent on invading their lake. Maurice is the only one who can bring peace.

episodes.name: Captain Cahouete
episodes.overview: But who is this Captain Cahouete pretending to be as brave as the Jungle Bunch and challenging the Grand Furax?

episodes.name: The Sand of Fire
episodes.overview: Maurice's stripes are wearing away and needs more paint, but the painter doesn't have anymore.

episodes.name: The Great Evil Itch
episodes.overview: Mama Dongo, an old meerkat, calls the Jungle Bunch to the rescue to find out about an itch that is driving the meerkats crazy.

episodes.name: The Striking Cry
episodes.overview: The Jungle Bunch find themselves trapped in a cage overlooking an island surrounded by hungry crocodiles... Fortunately, Maurice is the master of The Striking Cry.

episodes.name: Boiling Show
episodes.overview: Fred recruits some singers and is taken to the Rock of the Lynx. However, the lynxes want to get rid of him so they can become the only singers of the jungle.

episodes.name: Free Fall
episodes.overview: Join Maurice the penguin who thinks he's a tiger and his misfit friends as they embark on an adventure they will never forget!

episodes.name: The Little Plant of Horrors
episodes.overview: Marla, a crazy botanist, can't control the carnivorous plant she has created and it doesn't stop growing! The Jungle Bunch are sent in to destroy it.

episodes.name: The Devastation
episodes.overview: Termites have taken possession of the jungle, they destroy the trees and this causes a chain reaction.

episodes.name: The Lost Groove
episodes.overview: Fred has lost his groove and only Pelvis the koala, King of Rock, can help him find it. The only problem is that Pelvis is mostly king of the playback.

episodes.name: Daddy Miguel
episodes.overview: Join Maurice the penguin who thinks he's a tiger and his misfit friends as they embark on an adventure they will never forget.

episodes.name: Old Jim's Treasure
episodes.overview: The Jungle cave is brutally attacked by a horde of rampaging pirates: Dirty Beard and his gang are searching for Suzy, a young raccoon pirate, they want to retrieve the treasure map of his father's the Old Jim ... The Jungle Bunch go with Suzy in search of the treasure.

episodes.name: Junior's First Catch
episodes.overview: Join Maurice the penguin who thinks he's a tiger and his misfit friends as they embark on an adventure they will never forget.

episodes.name: The Strongest Animal in the Jungle
The Mystery of the Yellow Cave
The Show Must Go On
episodes.overview: Fred is kidnapped.

episodes.name: Dance of the Vultures
episodes.overview: The pals investigate when raccoons go missing.

episodes.name: Planet of the Ape
episodes.overview: A beaver asks for help when monkeys abduct his friends.
